quran[10{c,v,t}:
6,9,Wa law ja'alnaahu malakal laja'alnaahu rajulanw wa lalabasnaa 'alaihim maa yalbisoon
6,10,Wa laqadis tuhzi'a bi-Rusulim min qablika fahaaqa billazeena sakhiroo minhum maa kaanoo bihee yastahzi'oon (section 1)
6,11,Qul seeroo fil ardi summan zuroo kaifa kaana 'aaqibatul mukazzibeen
6,12,Qul limam maa fis samaawaati wal ardi qul lillaah; kataba 'alaa nafsihir rahmah; la yajma 'annakum ilaa Yawmil Qiyaamati laa raiba feeh; allazeena khasirooo anfusahum fahum laa yu'minoon
6,13,Wa lahoo maa sakana fillaili wannahaar; wa Huwas Samee'ul Aleem
6,14,Qul aghairal laahi attakhizu waliyyan faatiris samaawaati wal ardi wa Huwa yut'imu wa laa yut'am; qul inneee umirtu an akoona awwala man salama wa laa takoonanna minal mushrikeen
6,15,Qul inneee akhaafu in 'asaitu Rabbee 'azaaba Yawmin 'Azeem
6,16,Mai yusraf 'anhu Yawma'izin faqad rahimah; wa zaalikal fawzul mubeen
6,17,Wa iny-yamsaskal laahu bidurrin falaaa kaashifa lahoo illaa Huwa wa iny-yamsaska bikhairin fa Huwa 'alaa kulli shai'in Qadeer
6,18,Wa Huwal gaahiru fawqa 'ibaadih; wa Huwal Hakeemul Khabeer
